Spotlight: Abuse in the Catholic Church
========================================================
author: Andrew Ba Tran
date: November 11, 2015

2002
========================================================
On January 24, 2002, the Boston Globe published the Spotlight Team's analysis of John Geoghan's personnel file, which the newspaper had gone to court to make public. Following the Globe's January 6-7, 2002 articles, this feature was an important milestone in coverage of the crisis, increasing the public's understanding of diocesan documents and the mechanisms of priest transfers

